      "content": "i get the doctor thing but i really dont have time for an appointment right now and i know some people do high dose loading doses all the time. if i only do it for like 2-3 weeks to \"load up\" before spring, i dont see why i'd need a blood test first. it's just a vitamin, right? isn't it pretty standard to do a big boost like that when you're deficient?",
